item.description:
Incredible music, catered dinner buffet, a cash bar, and a great year end party with all your favorite volunteers. The HRT Band will perform with The Amazing Aerochix. Come join us for a fantastic night of fun! Lets fill the house for our cause and all meetup members and guests will pay only half price for Gold Circle tickets the best seats in the house. That price is actually what we pay for each dinner. 50/50 raffles contests and lots of fun leading up to our volunteer of the year award.

For tickets
